   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n062_trainer_lindsay-1-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Trainer Lindsay$<BR>Press <FONT color=#a82424>[F11]</FONT> and check the <FONT color=#a82424>Gift Box</FONT>~ If you need a horse, come to me~ OK?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-a" mid="63"><![CDATA[<html>What? What are you talking about?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="62"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>Hello. <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>. You must be a little used to adventures now. Actually I was waiting for this moment.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-a" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-b" mid="65"><![CDATA[<html>Yes. Can I ride horses too?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="64"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR><FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, you must have progressed to a certain level for me to introduce a friend to you. The friend is none other than <FONT color=#a82424>horse</FONT>. It's more of a companion rather than a pet. Have you seen other people riding a horse before?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-b" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-c" mid="67"><![CDATA[<html>That's right.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="66"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>Of course. You can ride horses when you reach <FONT color=#a82424>Level 15</FONT>. You cannot ride it in <FONT color=#a94407>dungeons</FONT>, <FONT color=#a94407>Dark Lair</FONT>, and<FONT color=#a94407>Nests</FONT>. You shouldn't take it to a dangerous place, right?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-c" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-d" mid="69"><![CDATA[<html>Yes.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="68"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>And while you're on the horse, you cannot do actions like talking to an NPC like me. You cannot pick items up or change to battle mode. But of course, you can loot items if you have a <FONT color=#a94407>pet</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-d" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-e" mid="71"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="70"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>Horses can be found in <FONT color=#a82424>inventory's [Pet＆Mount]</FONT> tab, and you can ride a horse by <FONT color=#a94407>right-clicking</FONT> on it. When you are mounted, the info will appear in <FONT color=#a82424>character window's mount</FONT>. Additionally, you can equip your horse with decorations like <FONT color=#a94407>saddle</FONT> and <FONT color=#a94407>trinket</FONT>. And it can be used easily when you register it as <FONT color=#7e12d2>non-battle mode shortcut key</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-e" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-f" mid="73"><![CDATA[<html>Please summarise in 3 sentences!</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="72"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>If you ride horses, your <FONT color=#a82424>movement speed</FONT> will increase so you would be able to move around town more easily. I will summarize it for you since I mentioned a lot of things. I heard that humans need summaries to understand.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-f" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-g" mid="76"><![CDATA[<html>Ok but… isn't this 4 sentences?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="74"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>Ok to summarize, <FONT color=#7e12d2><BR>* You can purchase horses at Trainer Lindsay or obtain them in nests.<BR>* Increases your movement speed.<BR>* Cannot be used in dungeons, Dark Lair, and nests.</FONT><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>* Can be registered in non-battle mode shortcut key.<BR></FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-g" image="QN_Npc_Woman_Trader_May.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-1" mid="78"><![CDATA[<html>Yes.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-h" mid="79"><![CDATA[<html>No I want to listen again.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="77"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>May</FONT> said you shouldn't care so much about small stuff like that.<BR>Now, shall I end the explanations here?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-h" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n033_archer_master_adellin-2-c" mid="81"><![CDATA[<html>Yeah.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="80"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Archer Adelynn$<BR>Okay. You can ride horses when you become Level 15. You can only use them in towns, world map, and guild wars. You cannot use them in dungeons, dark lair, or nests. You shouldn't bring them to dangerous places right?</html>]]></talk_question>
